    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……なるほど。
ルカ・ミルダにホットドッグを
買ってこさせればいいんだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I see.
I just need to have Ruca Milda go buy a hotdog.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なぁ、それ自分で買っちゃだめなのか？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I mean, can't you just that buy that on your own?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルカ・ミルダに買ってこさせた
ホットドッグは味も格別……らしい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It seems when Ruca Milda is the one to purchase
the hotdog, it ends up tasting exceptional.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ホントかな……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That right...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
